title: WW 2.2 Volume 1 - The Battle of Paris (2012) (phillywilly) cbr
description:
In the spring following Hitler's death, Chancellor Goring launches an offensive against Belgium and France. But the torrential rains which began shortly after hostilities commenced put an end to all hopes of a rapid victory. After the battle of Sedan, the Germans' main objective was the taking of Paris. The capital, emptied of all inhabitants, and occupied by small groups of French soldiers, waits... One of them will unknowingly play a decisive role in the coming battle...
